# Voting Resolution Flow

> **⚠️ Phase 2 Content:** The voting mechanics described in this document are **not yet implemented**. This documents the planned Phase 2 voting system for reference.

## Phase 1: What Actually Exists

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant PM as PredictionMarket
    participant Oracle as VotingOracle

    Admin->>Oracle: set_poll_status(poll_id, Locked)
    Note over Oracle: Stores status + timestamp

    Admin->>Oracle: set_poll_status(poll_id, Resolved)
    Note over Oracle: Status updated, timestamp recorded
```

**Phase 1 reality:**
- `VotingOracle.set_poll_status()` lets admin manually set any poll status
- No community voting, no consensus thresholds, no voter rewards
- Emergency withdrawal checks use the `updated_at` timestamp (7-day timeout)

## Planned Phase 2: Full Voting Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start[Match ends<br/>Voting begins] --> CheckVoters{For each voter:<br/>can_vote?}

    CheckVoters -->|yes| RecordVote[Record vote<br/>yes/no/unclear]
    CheckVoters -->|no| Skip[Skip voter]
    CheckVoters -->|already voted| Skip

    RecordVote --> TallyVotes[Update vote tally]

    CheckVoters --> MoreVoters{More<br/>voters?}

    MoreVoters -->|yes| CheckVoters
    MoreVoters -->|no| CalculateConsensus[Calculate consensus<br/>yes / (yes + no)]

    CalculateConsensus --> Consensus{consensus > 85%?}

    Consensus -->|yes| AutoResolve[Auto-resolve<br/>outcome]
    Consensus -->|no| CheckAdmin{60% <= consensus<br/><= 85%?}

    CheckAdmin -->|yes| AdminReview[Send to<br/>Admin Review]
    CheckAdmin -->|no| DisputeFlag[Flag as<br/>Disputed]

    AutoResolve --> EmitResolved[Emit PollResolved<br/>with outcome]
    AdminReview --> WaitAdmin[Wait for<br/>admin_verify()]
    DisputeFlag --> WaitDispute[Wait for<br/>multi-sig resolve]

    WaitAdmin --> AdminAction{admin_verify<br/>or reject?}

    AdminAction -->|verify| EmitResolved
    AdminAction -->|reject| DisputeFlag

    WaitDispute --> MultiSig{Multi-sig<br/>approval?}

    MultiSig -->|3 approvals| EmitResolved

    EmitResolved --> ClaimsOpen[Claims open<br/>for winners]

    ClaimsOpen --> End[Resolution complete]
```

## Consensus Calculation (Phase 2)

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Total YES votes] --> C{Yes %}
    B[Total NO votes] --> C
    
    C -->|A / (A + B) * 100| Result
    
    Result -->|&gt; 85%| Auto["Auto-Resolve<br/>YES wins"]
    Result -->|60-85%| Admin["Admin Review"]
    Result -->|&lt; 60%| Disputed["Disputed"]
```

## Voter Eligibility

| Condition | Can Vote? |
|-----------|-----------|
| Voted on this poll before | No |
| Staked on this poll | No |
| Voting window expired | No |
| Poll not in Voting status | No |
